3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible sub-category as the paper involves training CNN models on augmented datasets. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible sub-category as the paper deals with generating and manipulating visual media (face images). 
5. cs.GR (Graphics) is a less likely sub-category, but still possible as the paper involves generating realistic face images using graphics techniques.
